snippet.title: Smoking Simulator Promo Trailer
snippet.description:
Ever get stressed at work? Life too much of a hastle? Well just puff up with this game and I guarantee you'll have a great time! Live out your wildest smoking dreams in Smoking Simulator 2014!

This is on the 2014 Indie Game Maker Contest. If you like it 

Download and Vote. Thank you!
http://contest.rpgmakerweb.com/game/view/id/623#.U7Krl_ldWSp

A Game By Chad Calvert and Luis Serrano

Steam Greenlight:
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=284143277

Rage Music By Sorus
Sorus - MarshLands
http://sorusrocks.bandcamp.com
https://www.facebook.com/sorusrocks
http://sorusrocks.com
https://www.youtube.com/user/sorusrocks

If you like the music check us out.
